    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok thanks that makes sense. so if I get a kit and the ph is like 7.5 or something, what's the best way to bring it down? also is there any way to tell if something is actually \"stealing\" the nutrients from the soil besides just the color of the leaves?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
